ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisReappointment of JUDITH ANNE LAROCQUE of Hawkesbury, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission on an interim basis, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four months; and designation of JUDITH ANNE LAROCQUE as Chairperson of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission on an interim basis, for a term of four months.
